804
00:35:32,740 --> 00:35:34,540
You're never going to be able to get past them.

805
00:35:34,540 --> 00:35:36,641
That is good advice for contracting,

806
00:35:36,641 --> 00:35:37,961
and it's good advice for life.

807
00:35:37,961 --> 00:35:41,342
So I just want to thank you all so much.

